quran[12{c,v,t}:
43,11,aur jis ne aik andazay ke sath aasman se pani nazilkiya. phir hum ne is se shehar murda ko zindahkiya. isi terhan tum zameen se nikalay jao ge
43,12,aur jis ne tamam qisam ke hewanat peda kiye aur tumahray liye kashtiyan aur charpaye banaye jin par tum sawaar hotay ho
43,13,taakay tum un ki peeth par charh betho aur jab is par baith jao phir apne perwar-digaar ke ahsaan ko yaad karo aur kaho ke woh ( zaat ) pak hai jis ne is ko hamaray zair farmaan kar diya aur hum mein taaqat nah thi ke is ko bas mein kar lete
43,14,aur hum apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lout kar jaane walay hain
43,15,aur unhon ne is ke bundon mein se is ke liye aulaad muqarrar ki. be shak ensaan Sarih nashukara hai
43,16,kiya is ne apni makhloqaat mein se khud to betiyan len aur tum ko chunn kar betay diye
43,17,halaank jab un mein se kisi ko is cheez ki khushkhabri di jati hai jo unhon ne khuda ke liye bayan ki hai to is ka munh siyah hojata aur woh gham se bhar jata hai
43,18,kiya woh jo zewar mein parwarish paye aur jhagrre ke waqt baat nah kar sakay ( khuda ki ) beti hosakti hai ?
43,19,aur unhon ne firshton ko ke woh bhi khuda ke bande hain ( khuda ki ) betiyan muqarrarkiya.kiya yeh un ki paidaiesh ke waqt haazir they anqareeb un ki shahadat likh li jaye gi aur un se bazprs ki jaye gi
43,20,aur kehte hain agar khuda chahta to hum un ko nah pujte. un ko is ka kuch ilm nahi. yeh to sirf atklin dora rahay hain
43,21,ya hum ne un ko is se pehlay koi kitaab di thi to yeh is se sanad pakarte hain
43,22,balkay kehnay lagey ke hum ne apne baap dada ko aik raste par paaya hai aur hum unhi ke qadam bqdm chal rahay hain
